.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二十二<br />\n<br />\n中央人民政府所屬各部門、各省、自治區、直轄市均不得干預香港特別行政區根據本法自行管理的事務。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T05:40:32.000Z","msg":"習帝：一國兩制不走樣不變形。<br />\n因為一國兩制本來就不存在，根本唔會走樣同變形。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國都強調美國香港關係法係建基於聯合聲明，唔係強國任意解讀嘅基本法，您仲提基本法22條。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f7426fef700fcd3a6195919517ac4acdac33d1","tid":1158670,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T05:41:34.000Z","msg":"張圖好紅色警戒FEEL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即刻想搵返黎玩"},{"pid":"9a6b7c6c96f3c82983511b69d3dd93d0f331421a","tid":1158670,"uid":201605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63e964017f64b8f09be0b8fdd71cb49e9c4165d9","tid":1158670,"uid":236171,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:13:34.000Z","msg":"點解無人提基本法22條？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大佬公然違反基本法無人入佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二十二<br />\n<br />\n中央人民政府所屬各部門、各省、自治區、直轄市均不得干預香港特別行政區根據本法自行管理的事務。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T05:46:24.000Z","msg":"可否入稟發禁制今，中聯辦違基本法，禁止中聯辦運作?"},{"pid":"eb5cd070a7bb4ecd91b13013fac49e1a9a9fcbf2","tid":1158670,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T06:11:51.000Z","msg":"支那: 上街, 睇死你們垃圾周未行兩野,  平時沒使返工咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}